---
title: Chinese Salt & Pepper Chicken With Stir-fried Veggies on Garlic Rice
description: Watch out salt and pepper squid, because our chicken version is going to steal even your biggest fans! This has all the spicy flavour, but is pan-fried instead of deep-fried, and is so quick and easy that it's going to blow your mind.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chinese-salt-pepper-chicken-c27a74d5.jpg
